>"},{"pid":"bb7243057da318a0c10399e1b5a8830eb0097164","tid":2298323,"uid":244168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4821b2780eea81d24c29973d54d233b38ffdf28","tid":2298323,"uid":247518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T17:55:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://facebook.com/druccello\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fdruccello&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=a1f0e403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/druccello</a>"},{"pid":"2489588229532c3a4fd6ccd87b00f54b8179e808","tid":2298323,"uid":384534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T18:39:24.000Z","msg":"以前食過Seroxat<br />\n我諗食左一兩年左右自己唔聽話慢慢停左<br />\n<br />\n食左之後會有射精障礙 <br />\n性欲就冇乜特別下降<br />\n個人會好撚祥和 <br />\n但係變左對打機冇乜興趣<br />\n拖延症狀大幅減少<br />\n思覺敏感症狀大幅減少<br />\n依家停左一年左右 又好似有番啲敏感<br />\n屌 都唔知睇唔睇醫生好<br />\n<br />\n但係其實我鐘意個人燥底aggressive少少...<br />\n食左藥真係太祥和..."},{"pid":"4886e3c0ebc2965efc46c04bb4c6944b2ef0166b","tid":2298323,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1dbb6aedf9fa1153ce31a31d8f725e0aba0c0e","tid":2298323,"uid":244168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45ecb225dd08011702daa7895ff8f13aa955c9a2","tid":2298323,"uid":192465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:40:50.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲係咪懵仔藥食完好累好眼訓乜都做唔到就算<br />\n<br />\n對康復有冇幫助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"其實都係講平衡好處同唔好處<br />\n<br />\n真係有部份嘅抗精神病藥會影響認知<br />\n但係調返轉頭講<br />\n每一次精神分裂或者躁狂抑鬱復發<br />\n都會對腦部造成損傷，繼而影響認知<br />\n<br />\n所以而家好多新一代嘅抗精神病藥<br />\n慢慢都比舊嘅進步<br />\n少啲會影響認知能力<br />\n好像 abilify, rexulti"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"咁一般政府精神科醫生派果啲藥其實有有用<br />\n<br />\n係整到你溫溫燉燉定係會醫你"},{"pid":"7ccd3743a8b354c5cc6d09231618a3719aebb6cd","tid":2298323,"uid":244168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score